表格机器压力异常表的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('PressIsFlag')
and type = 'U')
drop table PressIsFlag
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: PressIsFlag */
/*==============================================================*/
create table PressIsFlag (
id int identity(1,1),
MachineNo varchar(50) collate Chinese_PRC_CI_AS null,
DispatchOrder varchar(50) null,
BeginCycle varchar(50) null,
EndCycle varchar(50) null,
constraint PK_PressIsFlag primary key ()
WITH (IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF) ON [PRIMARY]
)
ON [PRIMARY]
go
